022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-31T21:49:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223004868\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022158493\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221490996356\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022171798\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022rockets-don\u0027t-make-toast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, rockets-don\u0027t-make-toast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI added a module, now I just need the badge.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/156613-community-space-station-122/\u0026amp;\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRight-click on the image, and select \u0022copy image location.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGo to the top right of the page and click on your name, and then \u0022Account Settings.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClick on \u0022Signature,\u0022 and paste the image location. It should end in .jpg.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClick save.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"rockets-don\u0026#039;t-make-toast","CreatedById":171798,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-31T21:50:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthanks \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}